  "source": "// Register a new asset and mint some to the specified account.\nseiyaku RegisterAndMint {\n  kotoage fn register_and_mint() permission(AssetManager) {\n    // name, symbol, quantity (precision or supply depending on host), mintable flag\n    let asset = asset_definition!(\"62Fk4FPcMuLvW5QjDGNF2a4jAmjM\");\n    let symbol = \"ROSE\";\n    let qty = 1000;      // interpretation depends on data model (example only)\n    let mintable = 1;    // 1 = mintable, 0 = fixed\n    register_asset(asset, symbol, qty, mintable);\n\n    // Mint 250 ROSE to Alice\n    let to = account!(\"sorau’Šø1Np’Šā’ŠĢŃā▒’Šćq11p’Į│’Šś2’Į▒5’Šć’Į”iCJKjR’Šöz’ĮĘNMN’Šå’Į╣’ŠĢPC’Į│’ŠÖFv’ĮĄE9LBLB\");\n    mint_asset(to, asset, 250);\n  }\n}\n",
